ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v27.datatype

Class ERL

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractType
      • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractComposite
        • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v27.datatype.ERL
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Composite, Type, Visitable, Serializable

    public class ERL
extends AbstractComposite

    Represents an HL7 ERL (Error Location) data type. This type consists of the following components:

    • Segment ID (ST)
    • Segment Sequence (NM)
    • Field Position (NM)
    • Field Repetition (NM)
    • Component Number (NM)
    • Sub-Component Number (NM)
